official_title: Testing Scalable Communication Modalities for Returning Breast Cancer Genetic Research Results to African American Women
inclusion_criteria:
-Women in the BWHS previously included in the targeted breast cancer sequencing project
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 40 Years
exclusion_criteria:
* Women with known cognitive impairments
* Women with variant of uncertain significance (VUS) results from the sequencing study
